channel.title: Game crash at Interloper green tube
channel.description: Hi! Right now im at the part of the interloper chapter where you go inside the green tube. My issue is my game always crashes once i reach the 3 green aliens. Adjusting all my in game settings does nothing and i've verified my steam files. Is there any fix for this? Thank you.
